A beautifully written thread about our transformation through cancer.

We emerge from this chrysalis not as butterflies, but as Frankensteinian broken dolls.

Those around us move on.

But we are trapped in bodies that don't work, that betray us. Trapped in fear.

Love us. https://t.co/vF0W6uQkrR
